  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/14d88a247d27c3265286fc76eb410866.poster.avif?t=1773869365\" width=594 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/14d88a247d27c3265286fc76eb410866.webm?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/14d88a247d27c3265286fc76eb410866.mp4?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A peaceful exploration and base building game about recovering your late mentor’s work.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Base building</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/4185160c95f70b625d3fdcbbb6a4404c.poster.avif?t=1773869365\" width=594 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/4185160c95f70b625d3fdcbbb6a4404c.webm?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/4185160c95f70b625d3fdcbbb6a4404c.mp4?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect valuable resources, set up experiments, sell plant seeds, and expand your science outpost!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take care of your plants and experiments</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/f091cc66b4d6bb7280d7f2d39296fafa.poster.avif?t=1773869365\" width=594 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/f091cc66b4d6bb7280d7f2d39296fafa.webm?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/f091cc66b4d6bb7280d7f2d39296fafa.mp4?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Producing lots of crops and data will allow you to upgrade your base and buy new tools!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize your base and equipment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/509813d0e6781d265438d23e428acf73.poster.avif?t=1773869365\" width=596 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/509813d0e6781d265438d23e428acf73.webm?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/509813d0e6781d265438d23e428acf73.mp4?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/6604dad75e6c2a8458dc3c62fe534e0d.poster.avif?t=1773869365\" width=596 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/6604dad75e6c2a8458dc3c62fe534e0d.webm?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/6604dad75e6c2a8458dc3c62fe534e0d.mp4?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Apply new paint jobs and upgrades to your structures and your sled!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exploring</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/2fc0aa2056aefc836057f3b60c1387c5.poster.avif?t=1773869365\" width=594 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/2fc0aa2056aefc836057f3b60c1387c5.webm?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/2fc0aa2056aefc836057f3b60c1387c5.mp4?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover the many locations around the island, find antique objects and letters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Co-op</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/c770b0bb7122db44424b3927fc75ca22.poster.avif?t=1773869365\" width=594 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/c770b0bb7122db44424b3927fc75ca22.webm?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325210/extras/c770b0bb7122db44424b3927fc75ca22.mp4?t=1773869365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can do all of this with up to 3 other friends (4 players co-op mode)!",
